{"tid":1633823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"睇今晚黨鐵會唔會重兵註守就知政府心態","createTime":"2019-10-07T05:21:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T05:26:42.000Z","uid":27616,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f27decc5b6d1d172051df1e378fc50847c34b3ea","tid":1633823,"uid":27616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:21:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4204899b73d6e7fb8ff2113fd37cc95c500e52e","tid":1633823,"uid":167011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:22:16.000Z","msg":"罷工係對個政權最撚有衝擊既抗爭手法，但三罷做左咁撚多次，都係得8.5成功，因為計劃左好撚耐，對香港人黎講，個個都只想被罷工，到呢個地步，你仲想做休息撚，而唔乘勝追擊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勿拆黨鐵！！全民被罷工！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n三樣香港人應同樣憎恨既野：<br />\n政府、黑警、黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n呢三樣先係主線<br />\n你個啲乜鳩紅藍店，我理撚得你幾時搞？<br />\n個啲要休息，冇問題，但咁撚樣都唔食住上，令到全港自動罷工，咁我真係代表我全力支持既香港政府多謝你為香港既經濟服務<br />\n<br />\n唔撚係話和理非冇用，但和勇合一係成場運動既關鍵，兩樣一齊做唔撚得？講緊既係，拆鐵係唔撚會影響人權法，或所謂既民意，但對政權、運動係現時有最大既影響力"},{"pid":"8743fc53e5b6cdfcfb43229470c76745a1f9f794","tid":1633823,"uid":5031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:22:23.000Z","msg":"講得好 麻煩大家幫推<br />\n好多野可以做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［我要上熱門］明明講左長期開花先會贏點解又要休息<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633553\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633553</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8980943dee0bc13ad1185f7e70a778220a952910","tid":1633823,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:22:38.000Z","msg":"有時唔洗下下硬打既，轉個方式抗爭都得<br />\n比勇武叉叉電 比文宣組做下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631757\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631757</a>"},{"pid":"5cf0267365cc4bd08c2aaae19e3173fd4f2f0147","tid":1633823,"uid":288523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:22:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"834de15c61fb2b2e45e8e1c4c040b3ca8b7903d6","tid":1633823,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:26:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">又話杯葛？<br />\n又話抗爭？<br />\n繼續俾錢佢賺去出賣港人？<br />\n和理非平時返工唔好再俾正價搭黨鐵！<br />\n無得揀嘅情況例外</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/237n0J0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F237n0J0.jpg&h=61248f49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o0TeRHg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo0TeRHg.jpg&h=94f567e9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RFtRTVB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRFtRTVB.jpg&h=5322f0ae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vxJ20AB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvxJ20AB.jpg&h=c7141e62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JFpQ9Cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJFpQ9Cb.jpg&h=a7156522&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果和理非連咁小野都做唔到<br />\n就唔好學人話抗爭</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rHxjrJf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrHxjrJf.jpg&h=8688cd40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">聽日<span style=\"color: red;\">全民三罷</span>！！！<br />\n當十幾歲嘅學生中槍，<br />\n咁多個人冇咗隻眼，<br />\n咁多個義士死諫，<br />\n仲可以正常返工返學？</span>"}]}